Age-related macular degeneration masqueraders: From the obvious to the obscure.

Paez-Escamilla M(1), Jhingan M(2), Gallagher DS(1), Singh SR(2), Fraser-Bell 
S(3), Chhablani J(4).

Author information:
(1)Department of Ophthalmology, University of Pittsburgh Medical Center, 
