Chronic wounds: Current status, available strategies and emerging therapeutic 
solutions.

Las Heras K(1), Igartua M(2), Santos-Vizcaino E(3), Hernandez RM(4).

Author information:
(1)NanoBioCel Group, Laboratory of Pharmaceutics, School of Pharmacy, University 
